Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takahisa-senpai...
