Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Kakeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Yuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She fell asleep while we were out there in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I carried her into the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had lived up until now by thinking only about how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to become strong."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to become better at being an Onmyouji than anyone else."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I studied alone, ignoring everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lived while chasing after the legendary Onmyouji, \NKusakabe Misao, that I had known about since childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must've been so naive to think that I could have won...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That maybe I could have passed Misao the way I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so childish that it's pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She showed me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't win against Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:13:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in different leagues, Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misao and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misao had learned from experience with other people.{Misao ha taikan teki ni hito wo manabi jibun no naka ni torokondeita}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that, I have always secluded and taught myself alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had only yearned for knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a speculator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I don't have any experience, I imagine it in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The knowledge learned from paper and the sensation of learning through the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you think is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misao had read all of my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I could do was move in a way that gets easily read like the texts I've studied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. I believe that you're thinking too much into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pitiful speculator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why I was able to use the Aeon's Eye is thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me not through papers but through the sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't the first feeling you perceive when you meet the person you so admire be nervousness?{"wouldn't you be nervous if you met the person you admire so much?"/akogareta sonzai ni hajimete nen to mukatta toki de kinchou suru deshou ka}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so you end up not feeling like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, you can't stay calm about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I can't express it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Thank you, Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably in the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he'll come back soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit. Just a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty late. I'm gonna go look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took a walk around the garden. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, come here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. I liked Takahisa-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuka. You shouldn't just enter here without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hug me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A parallel world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To seal the Witch away, the disciples used a forbidden magic: \NThe Rainbow of the Covenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It splits and diverts the enemy's magic into seven worlds, thus weakening them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That skill was used 64 years ago to obstruct the Descent to Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in return, seven fragments were born and scattered to their respective parallel worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fragments were originally split into seven different worlds?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a scattered fragment was first thrown into the Crimson Night, the rest were all gathered together.{chiru not shiru ~MMC}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so for some reason, when the Crimson Night ended, all the fragments had again gathered into one world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is that world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell of that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That smell... I'll erase that smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say that there were fragments each in their own \Nrespective worlds, then to whom does this world belong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're here, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're here, everything is fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so too, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm around, everything is fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine without your big sister anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be surprised about. This Kukuri-san is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were someone that had originally held a fragment in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they can influence the world's structure with the power of the fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The illusion that Yuka-san created for Kakeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Kukuri-san that had held a fragment has already died in her own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this actually Yuka's world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You doesn't have to fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you to have appeared by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ever forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you going to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko went alone into the crystal tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine as long as you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka, did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of me that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My weapon is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt my Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I continued to fight because I wanted to protect you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are precious to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That feeling won't change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there's something else important to me right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, I'm coming now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko... Why did you have to go ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superbia, other fragments are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to heal your wounds, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was just the power of the fragment of Void that you hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.18,0:22:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have you turn back into a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:25.14,Default (higher vert pos),,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:37.37,Default (higher vert pos),,0000,0000,0000,,A fragment of Void...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:38.75,Default (higher vert pos),,0000,0000,0000,,She pulled it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.77,0:22:43.31,Default (higher vert pos),,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:40.68,Default (higher vert pos),,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.71,0:23:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pull out your right eye, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avaritia-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:23:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fragment...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.15,0:24:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
